\c 8
\s Ezira unovaravira murairo waJehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino vanhu vese vakaungana nomoyo umwe padare rakange riri pamberi pesuwo remvura; vakaudza Ezira munyori kuti auye nebhuku yomurairo waMozisi, wakange warairwa vaIsraeri naJehovha.
\v 2 Ezira mupristi ndokuuya nomurairo pamberi peungano yavarume navakadzi, navese vakange vachigona kunzwisisa, nezuva rokutanga romwedzi wechinomwe.
\p
\v 3 Akaravamo padare rakange riri pamberi pesuwo remvura, kubva mangwanani kusvikira masikati, pamberi pavarume navakadzi navese vakange vachigona kunzwisisa; nzeve dzavanhu vese dzikateerera mashoko ebhuku yomurayiro.
\p
\v 4 Ezira munyori akamira pakakwirira pakange pakavakirwa izvozvo namatanda; uye Matitia, naShema, naAnaya, naUriya, naHirikia naMaaseya vakamira kurutivi rwake rworudyi, naPedhaya, naMishaeri, naMarikiya, naHashumi, naHashibhadhana, naZekariya, naMeshurami vakamira kuruboshwe rwake.
\p
\v 5 Ezira akazarura bhuku pamberi pavanhu vese; (nokuti akange amire kumusoro kwavanhu vese;) zvino akati achizarura vanhu vese ndokusimuka.
\p
\v 6 Ipapo Ezira akavonga Jehovha, Mwari mukuru. Vanhu vese vakapindura, vachiti, Ameni, Ameni, vachisimudza maoko avo; ipapo vakakotamisa misoro yavo, vakanamata kuna Jehovha zviso zvavo zvakatarira pasi.
\p
\v 7 Jeshua, naBhani, naSherebhia, naJamini, naAkubhi, naShabhetai, naHodhia, naMaaseya, naKerita, naAzaria, naJozabhadhi, naHanani, naPeraya, navaRevhi vakadudzira vanhu mirairo; vanhu vakaramba vamire panzvimbo yavo.
\v 8 Vakarava zvichinzwika kwazvo mubhuku yomurairo waMwari; vakazvidudzira,,vakanzwisisa zvinorahwa.
\p
\v 9 Ipapo mubati Nehemiya, nomupristi Ezira munyori, navaRevhi vakadzidzisa vanhu, vakati kuvanhu vese, Zuva rino idzvene kuna Jehovha Mwari wenyu; musaungudza nokuchema; nokuti vanhu vese vakachema vachinzwa mashoko omurayiro.
\v 10 Ipapo akati kwavari, Endai henyu, mudye zvakakora, nokunwa zvinozipa, mugotumirawo migove kuna vasina kugadzirirwa chinhu nokuti zuva rino idzvene kuna She wedu; musava neshungu, nokuti mufaro waJehovha isimba renyu.
\p
\v 11 Naizvozvo vaRevhi vakanyaradza vanhu vese, vachiti, Nyararai henyu, nokuti izuva dzvene; musava neshungu.
\v 12 Ipapo vanhu vese vakaenda kundodya nokumwa, nokutumira vamwe migove, nokufara kwazvo; nokuti vakange vanzwisisa mashoko avakaparidzirwa.
\p
\v 13 Zvino pazuva rechipiri vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avanhu vese, navapristi, navaRevhi, vakaunganira kuna Ezira munyori, kuzoteerera mashoko omurayiro.
\v 14 Vakawana pakanyorwa mumurayiro, kuti Jehovha akaraira Mozisi, kuti vana vaIsraeri vanofanira kugara pamatumba pamutambo womwedzi wechinomwe;
\v 15 uye kuti vanofanira kuzivisa nokuparidza shoko iro pamaguta avo ose, napaJerusarema, vachiti, Budirai kugomo, mundotora matavi emiorivhi, namatavi emiorivhi yomusango, namatavi emimirite, namatavi emichindwe, namatavi emiti mikobvu, kuti muite matumba sezvakanyorwa.
\p
\v 16 Naizvozvo vanhu vakabuda, vakauya nawo, vakazviitira matumba, umwe neumwe pamusoro pedenga reimba yake, napavazhe dzavo, napavazhe dzeimba yaMwari, napadare resuwo remvura, napadare resuwo raEfuremu.
\p
\v 17 Ungano yose yavakange vakadzoka pakutapwa vakaita matumba, vakagara pamatumba; nokuti kubva pamazuva aJeshua mwanakomana waNuni kusvikira pazuva iro, vana vaIsraeri vakange vasina kuita izvozvo. Pakava nomufaro mukuru.
\v 18 Uye zuva rimwe nerimwe, kubva pazuva rokutanga kusvikira pazuva rokupedzisira, akarava pabhuku yomurairo waMwari. Vakaita mutambo mazuva manomwe; pazuva rorusere vakaita ungano yokupedzisira, sezvakange zvatemwa.
